basics.label: Aspiring Software Developer |  Computer Networks Intern at University of California, Irvine
basics.name: Nathaniel Louis Tisuela
basics.summary: Planning to graduate from UCI with a bachelor's degree in Computer Science, I am an aspiring software engineer with a current background in Information Technology.

work.summary: My programming background in Powershell, Python, SQL, and XML help maintain and inventory network machines. I troubleshoot and deploy new machines, implementing software such as Sonicwall, AOMEI, Acronis, and Dameware.
Onsite visits and remote support to clients to troubleshoot or maintain current software/systems, as well as deploying new systems to clients.

references.name: Erlich Bachman
references.reference: It is my pleasure to recommend Richard, his performance working as a consultant for Main St. Company proved that he will be a valuable addition to any company.
